beer.beer_description:
Manilita | Nelson | Motueka

It was only a matter of time before we released another TIPA and More Paua pushes away from the stonefruit and sweet citrus forward triples we’ve previously released to bright tropical fruit and the quintessential Nelson Sauvin character, gooseberry/white grape/passionfruit. Freestyle Manilita adds depth with layers of red berries.
